0 周年。他亲眼目睹了这座城市受到英国脱欧、疫情和两次能源危机的影响。但这并没有阻止他实施任何城市中最严格的空气质量法规。但他尚未成功建造足够的房屋，并努力不断改善火车网络。随着城市的不断发展，汗与阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 谈论了伦敦的成功和失败的教训。作为英国工党的杰出成员，汗也分享了他对该党未来的看法。采访录音于4月16日。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;立即收听，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/61fyX66llOeuxu5yacNIY3zbXvvFl8H2HfDVqaHVEfCLPWPuJNGy24f-ka-QJKhjdjCABT07C8rWI4Qm-i_fZ8FARElxj6LYO4ekGrK4P8TBAiqSr6nVzJFPsNmjfWudf1UetZoITA2eNtBi6JDsP5has9RYXLt6UxkuziwIVg1aj5ScelFLwqpYg1tiietwPUolsUGfReSDxlcsJdeF-d7dPy_OJdLRFqglvT1J5M_FO7BMuZvudq5dpSpcHkOXXyqBOFUWSOFsEZ0yIT0Bo-b9klBe2fzwXX8_zHMJW2y4YjU8Vv_UjEKtjR5H6h_1QS5r1A/L44W-A1v-A2muB6ERizHb3MlbzxSNWNW/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/C-RNSuGpLqh7vXkYdwuTIz11pu5c38yGgIb4U9gi78ui3u4GcW9A3ug953qrfMvukWs_OviikXgxk3Kb7bX8BsncdII2fxt26k9Dx0p35TVrCw2QX2GLB5YfgefrjQiuG-W0sGecbo9o22ZLQQKBD2KZSOwNsxwSXKFsopWSKTVMqkxxLvakZCDfIhuIe_FZ_lW2NTCuLZnZhAKgDChWzwR1LNSnmNElUq_7CMg8bwSnrA-flyDYQm6e7_wHYssoxRM8t06sOloaHq1jO7BSh4dXDYmrFOxJ5SJnkGxO5nNWCnekvSuOYI66s6v4Psj5XDj8bMuy27LDYiTbLhmI91oilX_o/Y10MEZLZRoJolgNGPA3ao3RE8dMkClAa/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/JZxzwzr91LP0bmYTdMNnR27WEJOuI1QibXDCw5VvJFB6ZgSzWy8Z5xdYin1lUuAhQhZa6DqsoVXUWhyr3VggjoL6h-g26zpJamH8ZiFLre_U_yHS9NyIbNatcecewmDUvODsskVcVrUKuPawmQa0pFOQaUby-zYBBIJp3gY-UwSjzRYKlenCnptaF3VbL8xtGvzLkb4wzV6kXHyXq3w0CmfrRKQYLxojpDMQabTV1O_i7QF70lC_HIJULYjQzSYvEtNgO17r5WH13fbedCy1DieNKG5kxHyF2SSIjD9Rw_pScSF01vjOlnpQGyCYmp0y_Ab9scP-wpJwYZiyzW2o4it58LRT/JNKCPerE0knZFiro6AqeBGj-nCnmAvjq/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;YouTube&lt;/a&gt;上订阅，即可每周四观看《零》的新剧集。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-to