p;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=17838787&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=04242026&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6" style="display: block; height: auto;" width="100%" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;全球必读&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;特朗普表示，以色列和黎巴嫩&lt;/strong&gt;将把停火期限延长三周，此举为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/SlGdOSj_zN-jXEYI0lsS8hkEHL51qttsm3tK1CGMxPh5DHm0Jedyuo8ntb3l4pZC_1m08rRBBMRwhAsEMyz23CPzKfuC_Nugv1FX2d_swnawgxvnvF6NuKZMHfjHigX2joDUr2E7qgcxfyqCeM4HkO-6dfJr7xu84RYS5CDascV0kPhyrFWiVFPp41yrQ4kB6s23ChTDMx6n5YfycfRkPPXuOLVz7zctpGyictZNOC-_FnUUsEYjhPb8JKzhvJN8O3mxqB2ZX_YPfcSajBXOPeJL835-aFFfpIeOq9HVVbmdjIm55aRBX1YSvB023qgrid1J5JnB9WMJbtVmCVcbF3U5C_52_vVjtSg2B46QadRZNalv0gPfoy4zpbE22t1swyFOESVjdU8KS-65QYKOxC331uAL_lexjOUUgJshIOl_2GAmvvZUNlnwaQzU1I3YSD5TU3oiSoWC6lKKBpFyqJdH3Rz_u-j41vHnLDhMWx_zU-Iyg84rs_dmqpAR5XIwxLUFiEg_6CGyj8A3NR9MTFk/kF04UFD9xJ2VE2WC9gjpbA-3GyEnEtsO/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普称以色列和黎巴嫩将延长停火期限"&gt;达成长期协议创造了空间&lt;/a&gt;，并消除了结束美国与伊朗战争的障碍。消息人士称，德黑兰同意更多面对面和谈的前景受到总统的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Ie82D5IA8HlZYC-PcJ5JPGeHgSnZFOE0B5zcvzMPxqI0bez-IFQKIc_zg8yRWTfBZj52w4IM6QcvWr_bk6gfPdyWeT7_qtJ-eR_FemEK2NShGOo3TEzF6X9G7YBGZW-WGkKFkhu83gADGdFjer1ChlHyaB3VzY2PZG1Yqd7Q4jUi7lmmKK8HEhjMlKZ2ZY1lgBLqlN8dR7dQvrZDLxoytm5WENOoI8J6f7gSTYWkNFGuKZmjhxY0Act9iNBPD6lQavdhhJNB5276pC-Aj1m1TyGCxuvyhAntsH3WQoZI5n15MFb23cMvsDBzLWFt0jxd5jHyHXB3fQA8YqVDScPqbM5Ucdwbk2eR3V4Q5nC17UzDKTK-25VGSzrfI63hrLhTWNh4-Lj2qIsVdcvQOS16xSLodytmlxrxbFf9GL33RjQ42U77b6SuYw1dZnuiJsf1TIweYW2kUl17debgGG0xPsbahcxfg4yZe58TULuvh8gCGSkoMsHz2C7y5nplesp2CO_PAjnNdLTiUcXjQhQRwHQ/piuXqhGAhFuy53L46fFmAck1DuQhhr68/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗谈判动摇之际，特朗普的信息闪电战让顾问们产生了分歧"&gt;威胁和傲慢的社交媒体帖子&lt;/a&gt;的阻碍，伊朗谈判代表称这些帖子的目的是羞辱其领导人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;中国国家主席习近平多年来一直&lt;/strong&gt;通过阻止台湾领导人的外交会议和参与全球组织来孤立台湾领导人——现在，他还试图让他们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/P_KeVeARIoI1qnLy9-nuADJprLzuh9yEBAMPfkWz0q7JONZwHSOWxDC840N7dCHmfxYpTZydpLHOBzm4d9HpBMrij-o5zO3HdXwpCu0LanK1yVKMYPmInXd89Ca4MFS302jviGY7SAJgxezbi8nQnpyAfopKgO8_O1H8KfARV9Cgmq8jOxlNwRy38zNL4hCkPtikiCuh5u_4OejOhvQKu8mlC0ycD0qBYu0_WqJPSnls1vVb1j9nGifYQQwmEZmKqllwUq6vPx-0P8vrhVOm0aaxg1_IldS7B2txUJ6MaJBoo4xGJ3cOgKpcvxgZ2c8XCCdYAXGL0vX-TOfduRr2kh0l-C3YcRyZrx0p-takwMftDIiiYHDjFjbuXKxqkE_848NMQVhcAXUUMfcTCrkG6A15CuFQcKE6y5fj9ePEilE7bA8o1U5tUYLeoofLrcXBfXU-P4zHXEnevN8zN63INV25XFnaPI-WczVKxhfeaVAizs9LylifgzGvXj3u3LZK5ES2YkNfd0wXmW8_wm7Z/cGpSXZVupYiPF8bwQm331-8b1PdFv4Go/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="习近平将外国空域武器化以孤立台湾"&gt;远离天空&lt;/a&gt;。在塞舌尔、毛里求斯和马达加斯加在中国的要求下最后一刻决定吊销飞越许可证后，赖清德总统被迫取消了对斯威士兰罕见的国事访问。斯威士兰是该国在非洲的唯一盟友。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_4ugGHekt38/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_4ugGHekt38/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;从北京方面的角度来看&lt;/strong&gt;，特朗普十多年来首次访华的基础将比他六个月前上次会见习近平时&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/AA4PfqGzPSFemMHIf1Y3JLVdiiUmhx13uhrL-6klIs3kohO-xDcXTyMDmYrzyboxNU0rr844kdKRbpr-mgE3XihplLCDLiYBqhxKLKcJyQ2gkBtZ8IVRowqKayJ4n8mVLIim2xIJ22F1yFD1zCMD_FeVa5YxMnSOFnf3I9H6J6D0e1h-Y3pu-5Eyj3VY8h_D3I_qQlGvahOLz-DEGtv7Ex5hDGC4PhA4N72Iz9NnDHimaCXBLAoKpmJX_30jylGwReWdJdd6hpMNs8AViEy5xE4LtFxBhbQxE7YVYMBItgbKNovNwu41TeDuDyfgYX_mTt5H1GMvJgCJNJJ1xhL2qS0sTJ6KouCAEGgOH24VjjStPYuNyjuxLMvoMsEkgKRAIi6kXLz88X7qsbBbgWGL2rA8ShY9Re-wC6WttF_o2anWvO3e6GdcjH2gIMinfTVlLb8KmofeZcqxkr4IPvCkNkIH5Eq6tQ7wWmfeGJTLPcRkvsI8MJL_SzRopG2uq3YeESleH3yVnFTCbSdCvUNGJg/lr-hb66v-ztZ1FC-p4U1CPxuhTisez0c/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普陷入了全球经济战争。习近平已做好准备"&gt;的基础要弱得多&lt;/a&gt;。这是因为，自重新掌权以来，美国总统第二次测试自己对主要对手的影响力，并错误判断了回应。我们分析了如果伊朗战争不再推迟的话，五月中旬的旅行将会发生什么。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;欧盟领导人表示&lt;/strong&gt;，乌克兰开始第一阶段&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/wlAQ6HRUKnHi5x0LGQkc4-cpN8UDn8RwuzgAjl2t3OkFjSQp1MXpqaXQUTgDjsB0buDKg_w55-6L2Ri0BuElVRaMKP6StneqJfhkZqV6EB8O3GHnI1x0nVV3jVOQZBeQT4RrCRR3hKWvYSs0SEBn9RQSPsmY9LH1Ao7R9RjMumxOayqrD6BMPXoVtgEDhuE-_LJaDMgObLK8FZ4rZtprZDwIpAgwHVxZHRDmvPAO16uA5sgRdLbj1oTytGfRKEvVew3edeJO-qidFyiauEZff9ld5S8SDg1NaxcR7hUyOLUxg_PL5L07HFyKjOutdgPqqudYjD6iqyXke_G2iLzOrR36zpUWNRe4hgZWSquCR8kxt6ho-q2G9tsBlcCELUKUlXLkdfs0Y8-66_VJ59QOVofzY_pcwdqZNyqQas_5RJJZzvyAGqyEE-i6_VkAnQKAoqyjkVFrUrLqI-XlM1UDlK1frhbu9mIz5I51ZDBiqYsO4NGOXLQQkoVd8lxFyhgIE6Ulssub50MPkwEL3Q/9Cs4R4xHIeZWPThHQc_lqgGyYsHi3tTG/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="欧盟为与乌克兰就下一步入盟步骤进行谈判敞开大门"&gt;入盟进程&lt;/a&gt;的初步条件已经具备，这将推动总统泽伦斯基加入欧盟的努力，尽管具体日期的任何承诺仍难以确定。虽然特朗普表示，弗拉基米尔·普京&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/aIS4VFWXBNNEomc8OJWiR1yMmFg4MpPzqFakX6DeygmY8hF4FCz7rM7FHsoDGX00ARvUWLQMkseRDUq1viGbJ2ix6vmwrNYrCZ-VB1TChoF_Qx7shcBBqmQFNWRnBIg0dhKt-wEGb4qySnEG4P0r9k9lNzmC-j2i1klc0nOS6sePmEdN4biBMFn