24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;她希望国防工业能够通过利用不断飙升的全球需求来蓬勃发展，从而为日本军队提供更强劲的本土材料供应。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;时机似乎已经成熟。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;中东和乌克兰的冲突正在推动创新和秩序。高市正在向日本公司提供政府资金，用于投资国防研发。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;中国已经注意到这一点，并就东京过去遭受的军国主义死灰复燃发出警告。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;国内对此举动有些担忧：最近的一项民意调查发现，67%的受访者反对武器出口。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;但向&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/5klvMwtzA0TuBZnDXK6rMYGHp63g0aOc-xSfppyv_Fq8QSomsRm8zKu_AewlNba2g3w85XHw97ffEqjiL5pHGR1kcuwouFR_fRHD3pCzDKoPri-Mj44xSJXFGGKbICMHK6CUUyeX9AQHQtNzJhRoPGHEMPCDWLg07roDk7FVvEJAyvEpGaHygPfhQsYGu5b8JmZ97aAWlxJmM4wTI7T0Zkyb5swR_CQwkURM3uuX736ad-7ln09RXyImj6nOPC3hMQK4j6-buvZyixmmQhUFAWuwEDy_lnJXJU-G6ta7h1ziLJtuhAprj0eSELvxryYAQj4097dD-TYRdYBEjl1K8Sp12q-5EK7POdSQG5J2uUNzQQKi-hB0LYa6a82i3DBuK3F-FtdR-4kO0BxJsRApvHSs-AhqucOoL_IsEtbMqq3CGPCEb4AEta73_f-80g-usnjyplGKqoFFfyNjfhUW4f7beRglkLi3QoqcYfn8NMk2BrBBT2JM0g8wNszghdwDvzBDvpSucmWojPIo/ZAlFqCA1J8TjDbTTs1prV6DXanRh8LFd/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="澳大利亚签署从日本购买首批军舰的协议"&gt;澳大利亚提供军舰的&lt;/a&gt;一项大交易已经完成，高一的批准也得到了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/prrz2JAe-uMgCZ3ZQ4UcuCGeQVNbmoS0Eci2or76AGnKaje0kOnDF0g9TUyZWYtmvFU8mFfsTm3dx36K9fjsPe2v4jswwTMJ-5FOLMTZ-yqWrNW_ogdW_-YsuaulYOY_3zSoDcI7KZ9Iluek_p33WiVXnboJvsyoSCctq8h3oKhOhUYxqB-0z8j32tXtLxh0tNitpaOzaoFYQ96HOm_QbjVWIRuUoacDOC9owjdoALYqioxW-dwJzieLKxzf8Lcf6w61tk4tPTlYranev745IAuZEJnUhmk5zThXd1KsI_dVPh-PZRUxfIA6vC3IfMzsZtdcnx1LsqQFuD1YPi0Ix8iKELN13XzNuOJ0lRmUuS5uaCc6b7oKCWXDgRIJx3pjqvevOva7imENi3BFmz3nsp_VoNOkutldEKgil9V_urKlssHPFScqdySOuzgCFGuMUg8WaTWVgfOxssmRRYdPI93K6Bj1jTuzzlIqO8PdsScnIv1WNrfyGkjKFdPz80OMbHF_RMavPwJZWe8c4bvc6jQ/9FZfSNCwmbRD80l-S14AXhbzoEi0KCCH/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="高一的评